Grab MXE cross compiler (mxe.cc):

sudo git clone https://github.com/mxe/mxe.git /opt/mxe
sudo make -C /opt/mxe gcc zlib jpeg png bison bz2 freetype

Install Python 2.7.5 from python.org on nearby Windows (virtual) machine, copy C:\Python27 to /opt/mxe/Python27.

Add MXE to path:

export PATH="/opt/mxe/usr/bin/:$PATH"

And start build process:

make win32